title: Worst Date Wednesday: I Always Wondered What These Apartments Looked Like
description: She went on a date with a guy she connected with on Facebook from college.  He said they should "catch up".  It turns out they didn't have much to catch up on.  This was before smartphones so it involved getting lost and the line he used to try to come inside when he dropped her off is priceless.
